# Skill daemon working dir.
#
# This directory is created and owned by scripts/skill_daemon.py (M2+).
# It holds non-versioned runtime state:
#
#   skill_daemon.db          sqlite (runs, triggers, actions, cost)
#   skill_daemon.log         structured JSONL log
#   daemon.sock              unix socket for control commands
#   daemon.disabled          presence => daemon exits within one tick
#   proposals/<id>.md        dry-run optimizer proposals (M3)
#
# Everything except this .gitkeep is gitignored. See .gitignore.
